headline: Does the 23andMe Acquisition Make Regeneron a Buy Now?
summary: On May 19, Regeneron agreed to acquire 23andMe for $256 million.  At its peak, 23andMe's market value swelled to $5.8 billion.  Recently, Regeneron (NASDAQ: REGN) entered an agreement to acquire 23andMe for $256 million, which is a tiny fraction of its previous market value.
